  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div data-lake-element=\"root\" class=\"lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-parser-by=\"lake2html\"><a name=\"开启-Debug-模式\"></a><h2 id=\"68f3f46b\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">开启 Debug 模式</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">在 dockerd 配置文件 daemon.json（默认位于 /etc/docker/）中添加</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%223034e093%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22json%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%7B%5Cn%20%20%5C%22debug%5C%22%3A%20true%5Cn%7D%22%7D\" id=\"3034e093\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">{\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">  \"debug\": true\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">}</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">重启守护进程。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22598c6b37%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20sudo%20kill%20-SIGHUP%20%24(pidof%20dockerd)%22%7D\" id=\"598c6b37\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ sudo kill -SIGHUP $(pidof dockerd)</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">此时 dockerd 会在日志中输入更多信息供分析。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><a name=\"检查内核日志\"></a><h2 id=\"18126345\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">检查内核日志</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22499f5d58%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20sudo%20dmesag%20%7Cgrep%20dockerd%5Cn%24%20sudo%20dmesag%20%7Cgrep%20runc%22%7D\" id=\"499f5d58\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ sudo dmesag |grep dockerd\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ sudo dmesag |grep runc</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><a name=\"Docker-不响应时处理\"></a><h2 id=\"400eab8a\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">Docker 不响应时处理</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">可以杀死 dockerd 进程查看其堆栈调用情况。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%224f435ee7%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20sudo%20kill%20-SIGUSR1%20%24(pidof%20dockerd)%22%7D\" id=\"4f435ee7\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ sudo kill -SIGUSR1 $(pidof dockerd)</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><a name=\"重置-Docker-本地数据\"></a><h2 id=\"544ac026\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">重置 Docker 本地数据</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><em>注意，本操作会移除所有的 Docker 本地数据，包括镜像和容器等。</em></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%224bfd8b85%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20sudo%20rm%20-rf%20%2Fvar%2Flib%2Fdocker%22%7D\" id=\"4bfd8b85\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ sudo rm -rf /var/lib/docker</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div>",
